
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-stephan-cdni-usecases-metadata-00.txt'>
    <title>"metadata for CDNs Interconnection", Gilles Bertrand, Fieau Frederic, Pages Remi, Stephan Emile</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-stephan-cdni-usecases-metadata-00.txt</link>
    <description>There are use cases where the delivery of contents by a CDN on the behalf of another requires the exchange of extra information between these CDNs.  This memo proposes a RESTful framework for the exchange of content distribution metadata between an upstream and a downstream CDN.  Then it applies this framework to the use cases selected by te CDNi WG [I-D.ietf-cdni-use-cases] to identify relevant operations, objects and information elements of the CDNi metadata interface and to verify that the RESTful approach suits for these operations.</description>
    <dc:date>2011-10-23T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
